cf313329bf04614ff2187580bc8c717b794ce7d3.query:
SELECT
                users.user_id as id,
                users.active,
                users.admin,
                users.username, 
                passwords.password,
                address_books.ab as address_book
            FROM
                users
                INNER JOIN passwords
                    ON passwords.user_id = users.user_id
                INNER JOIN address_books
                    ON address_books.user_id = users.user_id
